A sample .gitignore file for Scala/sbt projects
By Alvin Alexander. Last updated: January 24, 2023

This is a sample Git .gitignore file that I use for Scala sbt projects:

# bloop and metals
.bloop
.bsp
.metals
project/metals.sbt

# vs code
.vscode

# scala 3
.tasty

# sbt
project/project/
project/target/
target/

# eclipse
build/
.classpath
.project
.settings
.worksheet
bin/
.cache

# mac
.DS_Store

# other?
.history
.scala_dependencies
.cache-main
exif.config

# general
*.class

target/
.bsp/
.idea/
.metals/
.bloop/
project/target/
project/project/
